Species of 
<taxonomicName box="[492,625,1821,1843]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Japanagallia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="89" pageNumber="90" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[492,625,1821,1843]" italics="true" pageId="89" pageNumber="90">Japanagallia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
: 437–443. 
<taxonomicName authority="C.A.Viraktamath, 2011" authorityName="C.A.Viraktamath" authorityYear="2011" box="[744,994,1821,1843]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Japanagallia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="89" pageNumber="90" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nepalensis" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[744,994,1821,1843]" italics="true" pageId="89" pageNumber="90">Japanagallia nepalensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1002,1085,1821,1842]" pageId="89" pageNumber="90">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1002,1085,1821,1842]" pageId="89" pageNumber="90" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
: 437. Male pygofer, lateral view; 438. Pygofer process as seen in the direction of arrow in Fig. 437; 439. Anal collar process, lateral view; 440. Aedeagus, lateral view; 441. Ventral process of aedeagus, posterior view in the direction of arrow in Fig. 440; 442. Style, dorsal view; 443. Connective, anterodorsal view; 444–450. 
<taxonomicName authority="C.A.Viraktamath, 2011" authorityName="C.A.Viraktamath" authorityYear="2011" box="[548,794,1913,1935]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Japanagaliia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="89" pageNumber="90" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="peculiaris" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[548,794,1913,1935]" italics="true" pageId="89" pageNumber="90">Japanagaliia peculiaris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[804,889,1913,1934]" pageId="89" pageNumber="90">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[804,889,1913,1934]" pageId="89" pageNumber="90" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
: 444. Male pygofer, lateral view; 445. Connective, anterodorsal view; 446. Style, connective and aedeagus, lateral view; 447. Aedeagus, ventrolateral view showing broad aspect of lateral process of shaft; 448. Aedeagus, anterodorsal view in the direction of arrow in Fig. 447. 449. Style, mesolateral view; 450. Style, dorsal view.
